                "maximum_value": 10.0,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Uncertainty of extracting peak",
                " area from pulse height spectrum (5-10%).",
                " A straight-forward error analysis produces symmetric",
                " errors; imposing the constraint that the 153 keV",
                " resonance was definitely observed in the TOF spectrum",
                " leads to the asymmetric errors."
              ]
            }
